   <talk_paragraph index="n2063_sorceress_anna-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Soceressanna.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2063_sorceress_anna-accepting-acceptted" mid="30" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Anna$<BR>It's a herb you have to get from the far north, so it won't be easy to get in a normal shop.<BR>
I hope you have a good connection in Merca City.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2063_sorceress_anna-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Soceressanna.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2063_sorceress_anna-1-" mid="32" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Anna$<BR>I have to go check on Shalica again, so please find the ingredients.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>※Go to Vernicka in Merca City.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-a" mid="34" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>... It's been a while since I've seen that face.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-a" image="QN_Salica_Chlid.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-b" mid="36" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Don't worry. It's not bad news.<BR>I came to let you know that Shalica finally woke up. I haven't met her in person yet,<BR>but she's better now, according to her caregiver.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-c" mid="38" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Somehow I'm not satisfied with them simply saying she's okay.<BR>Does this mean I should go and see her in person if I'm worried?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-d" mid="40" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>There's no need to overthink it like that. It's not what I meant.<BR>The fever hasn't gone down all the way yet though, so we need </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>icicle grass for medicine</FONT><FONT color=#662500>.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>The ingredients we need are written here, so take a look.</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Hands over the paper from Sorceress Anna.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-e" mid="42" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>... I see. I'm relieved you felt you could come here when in need of something.<BR>Anything else I need to know? For example, <FONT color=#a82424>why a Child would have a fever?</FONT> Something like that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-e" image="QN_Child_Grele.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-f" mid="44" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(I'm glad he's on my side. The guy sees right through me. It gives me the chills.)<BR>According to her caregiver, the same thing happened when she was </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>nursing another Mutant Child</FONT><FONT color=#662500>.<BR>It's a symptom that a Child experiences when it absorbs a jewel stronger than her own capacity.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-g" mid="46" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Shalica absorbed a jewel? That's even <FONT color=#a82424>stronger than her</FONT>?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-h" mid="48" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I'm sure you've already heard... what happened with the Cup of Healing.<BR>The Cup of Healing swallowed the jewels of Grele and Hiver and then brought Shalica back.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-i" mid="50" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>So, is that jewel you're talking about some kind of synthesized version of those absorbed by the Cup of Healing? <BR>A combination of the <FONT color=#a82424>Frozen Dragon's</FONT> jewel and that of the <FONT color=#a82424>Mutant Child</FONT> once called the hope of the Anti-Goddess Faction...?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-i" image="QN_Child_hiver.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-j" mid="52" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Indeed, and considering what Hiver got up to,</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>it could be at least half the jewels that the Childs were fighting over in the Western Territory</FONT><FONT color=#662500>.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>Whether Shalica absorbed part of them or the entire lot, it's no wonder she's having trouble coping.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2" mid="54" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka's eyes glare coldly.)</FONT><BR>I will have to look into just who is aware of this situation.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" mid="56" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I know what you're thinking, but stop looking at me like that. You're giving me chills.<BR></FONT><FONT color=#a82424>It's a short list: Norfe, her caregiver in Rhadames, me, and you.<BR></FONT><FONT color=#662500>That's all I know for sure, but I don't think Norfe would have informed anyone else about it.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" mid="58" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="57"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I see… Thank you for the confirmation.<BR>In that case, you're the one I should be most wary of right now, then, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" mid="60" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="59"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Ugh, you crazy fool.<BR>What is it that you expect of me? Do you really think I'm going to go running around flapping my mouth about this? Are you serious?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" image="QN_hwaran.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" mid="62" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="61"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Then put me at ease.<BR>What are you going to report back to <FONT color=#a82424>your employer</FONT> at Red Lotus Palace?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" mid="64" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="63"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>……</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" image="QN_Kanna.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-f" mid="66" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="65"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Don't tell me you forgot.<BR>Your friend, the <FONT color=#a82424>healer girl</FONT>, is still there, is she not?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-g" mid="68" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="67"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I've been working hard in the Western Territory, Vernicka. Things have been difficult.<BR>I honestly haven't given much thought about Shalica's condition or planned any further than letting you know what's going on.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-h" mid="70" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="69"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-i" mid="72" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="71"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What would you like me to say? I'm sure Hwaran will ask.<BR>It's good for her that all three Childs aiming for the Western Territory were wiped out at once, but she'll wonder what happened to those jewels.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-j" mid="74" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="73"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>It's a topic that most Childs are interested in. The Commander won't be an exception.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-k" mid="76" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="75"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I don't suppose claiming ignorance about the jewels' whereabouts will do the trick, right?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-l" mid="78" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="77"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Reporting that you witnessed the end of the Western Childs, yet somehow don't know where their jewels went?<BR>
Either one of them is a lie, or they're both lies. <BR>
If a mercenary I was hiring gave me as fishy a report as that, I'd start investigating him immediately. <BR>In that case, it wouldn't take long to find Shalica's trail.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-m" mid="80" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="79"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>This is driving me crazy.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-n" mid="82" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="81"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Maybe the only way is to shut you up for good.<BR><FONT color=#a82424>If there's no one around to give a report</FONT>, the jewels' whereabouts will naturally remain hidden.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-o" mid="84" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="83"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>That's not funny! Imagine telling jokes at a time like this!<BR>This is bad… No matter how I explain Hiver's disappearance, I won't be able get a jewel big enough to satisfy Hwaran</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>on such short notice.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-p" mid="86" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="85"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I agree. It's not a problem that can be solved by getting another jewel.<BR>We're going to have to make some excuse for their disappearance.<BR>Maybe you'd be better off telling her that either <FONT color=#a82424>Nephrite or Kaunos ran away</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-q" mid="88" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="87"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>That won't do. I'm not Hwaran's only informant. She'll soon find out it's a lie.<BR>I can't discredit myself like that. I need a more plausible excuse.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-r" mid="90" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="89"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>A plausible excuse... If there's <FONT color=#a82424>something Hwaran especially cares about</FONT>, why don't you make use of it?<BR>Whether a human or a Child, people tend to believe stories involving topics they're interested in.<BR>
Everyone likes the idea of killing two birds with one stone, after all.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-r" image="QN_DarkRubinat.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-s" mid="92" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="91"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Anything Hwaran is interested in is a big deal, though. It would be laughable to use Kyle as an excuse,</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>and we can't say the Blue Clan… or Ultima took it...</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>But... what about the </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Red Child?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-s" image="QN_DarkRubinat.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-t" mid="94" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="93"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Isn't the <FONT color=#a82424>Red Child</FONT> already a servant of the Goddess? I don't think you'll be able fool her long with that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-t" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3" mid="96" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="95"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>But other than him, there's no one who fits...</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>Were there any Childs in Rhadames who might make sense...? Hang on!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-a" mid="98" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="97"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I got one. </FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>I don't know what he is exactly, but even amid all that chaos in Rhadames, he had enough power to make<BR>Hiver and Kaunos stand back as soon as he appeared. He should be good enough.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-b" mid="100" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="99"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>You met a Child like that in Rhadames? Why didn't you tell me before?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-b" image="QN_Npc_geraint_Kid.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-c" mid="102" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="101"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Because he's a Child you already know of.<BR></FONT><FONT color=#a82424>The little golden-haired kid</FONT><FONT color=#662500> who hangs out with the Lagendian. He's connected to the Red Child somehow, right?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-d" mid="104" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="103"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Ah, the <FONT color=#a82424>golden-haired Dragon</FONT>...<BR>
He too is a Lagendian Dragon, which makes him similar to the Red Child as a matter of course.<BR>So you're going to tell her that he was there? And that he took the jewel?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-e" mid="106" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="105"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>It's perfect. Hwaran will probably take my word for it with such a plausible excuse.<BR>And he's </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>really disappeared</FONT><FONT color=#662500> anyway. I don't think even Hwaran will be able to find him.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-f" mid="108" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="107"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Disappeared? Where to?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-g" mid="110" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="109"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>That's something I'm better off in the dark about. Maybe he's already gone back to Lagendia?</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>I don't need to know, to be honest. Okay, I think I have an idea of how I need to frame this.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#a82424>I might drop a hint that he's a new creation of the Goddess, like the Red Child.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-g" image="QN_Kali.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-h" mid="112" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="111"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Kali</FONT> wouldn't be too happy if she found out, but I can't think of a better way right now.<BR>All right, I'll leave Hwaran to you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-i" mid="114" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="113"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>He's a Lagendian Dragon, so a little attention from Hwaran shouldn't be enough to bother him much.<BR>Just make sure you don't tell them anything first. If there's a problem, I'll let them know personally.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-j" mid="116" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="115"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Fine with me. And...<BR>If you have <FONT color=#a82424>any other information from Rhadames</FONT> besides the thing about the jewels, I recommend you mix it in<BR>
with your story when you tell Hwaran.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-k" mid="118" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="117"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>That's what I was going to do. </FONT><FONT color=#662500>Smart people like her who do a lot of thinking are </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>prone to let their imagination run wild</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#a82424>if you give them a lot of information at once,</FONT><FONT color=#662500> right?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-l" mid="120" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="119"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I suppose that's the same approach you take with me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-m" mid="122" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="121"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I haven't forgotten that you were thinking about locking me away in Merca until just recently, pal.<BR>Anyway, I better get a move on so I can get this information to Hwaran while it's still fresh.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-m" image="QN_Hologram.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-n" mid="124" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="123"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I'll have the ship ready to leave immediately. I need to prepare the <FONT color=#a82424>herb</FONT> for Rhadames as well, so it seems I finally have something concrete to do.<BR>As much as I don't like it, I'll have to <FONT color=#a82424>work closely with Norfe</FONT> for the time being.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
